# 🛰️ Sextant Orbital Resilience Framework (SaaS API)

A deterministic simulation platform for modeling dependency-driven cascade behavior in complex distributed systems.

---

# 🧭 Overview

This system provides a **SaaS API layer** over a deterministic simulation engine that models:

- Dependency graphs
- Cascade failure propagation
- Risk scoring
- System resilience analysis

---

# ⚙️ Core Modules

## API Layer
- FastAPI gateway
- Authentication middleware
- SaaS routing

## Core Engine
- Deterministic simulation engine
- Graph-based execution model
- Cascade propagation system

## SaaS Layer
- API key authentication
- Tier-based usage limits
- Request tracking system

